To
No.1/34/2/2020-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
The undersigned is directed to say that consequent upon the demise of Shri Ramvilas
Paswan, Minister of Consumer Affairs, Food and Public Distribution on the 8th October, 2020, Shri
Piyush Goyal assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of Consumer Affairs, Food and Public
Distribution. He will continue to hold the charge of the office of the Minister of Railways; and Minister
of Commerce and Industry.
Bege
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded for information to the Vice-Chairperson, NITI Aayog.
Copy forwarded for information to:
Secretary to the President.
Secretary to the Vice-President.
Copy also forwarded for information to :
Principal Secretary to the Prime Minister.
Principal Adviser to the Prime Minister.
MOST IMMEDIATE
New Delhi, the 9th October, 2020
*JK*
400 Copies.
